body:
This game is pretty straight forward,
All you have to do is type out a sentance and say which part of your body you used to type it.
Remember, no hands and you cant delete anything you type!
Try to be creative and try something no one else has
Please keep the comments appropriate!
Me first!:
I olve cookies they br awesaome. typed by my nose
